    "Instead, the important predictors are mostly indicators for judge birth cohort, which is mechanically related to attendance timing due to the dierences in when the judges were appointed.",
    "These covariates are collinear with judge xed eects, so they cannot be included directly in our regressions as controls using post double selection (Belloni et al., 2014).",
    "Instead, we will adjust for the elastic-net-selected characteristics that predict the timing of attendance, fully interacted with year xed eects.",
    "For example, we allow judges born in the 1940s to have a dierent intercept in each year.",
    "Besides endogenous timing of attendance, we are also concerned about endogenous selection of judges to cases."
